    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a living dream where time stands perfectly still. This exquisite machine is a masterclass in preservation, boasting a luster so deep it feels like looking into a still mountain lake. Every stitch in the supple leather tells a story of meticulous care, and the engine's purr is a symphony of engineering excellence that hasn't aged a day. This isn't just a car; it's a preserved legacy, a rare opportunity to own a piece of history that remains as flawless and breathtaking as the moment it was born. To drive it is to command the road with a grace that only a true masterpiece can provide.",
      "price": 48500.0,
